{"about_the_game":"This classic 4X strategy game has survived for more than 25 years thanks to the devotion of dedicated fans and modders. Now you too can enjoy Emperor of the Fading Suns, renowned for its deep game play and unparalleled setting. First released in 1997, this is the Enhanced version of the game released on its 25th anniversary with significant upgrades and improvements.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Battle on land, air, sea and space as you fight for control of humanity\u2019s known worlds as one of five Royal Houses. <br></li><li>Utilize combined arms tactics to overcome enemy positions.<br></li><li>Use a robust diplomacy engine to trade technologies, political offices, threats, favors and even votes for the imperial crown. <br></li><li>Enjoy a powerful economic engine that allows you to trade any of the dozens of resources you develop. <br></li><li>Avoid the machinations of the Church and the anger of powerful alien races. <br></li><li>Recruit legions of theurigists, psychics, mutants, warbeasts and more.</li></ul><br>Modders have been enjoying this game for years, and this build ships with everything you need to create your own star-spanning maps and campaigns.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736715279","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799350/page.bg.jpg?t=1736715279","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799350/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736715279","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799350/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736715279","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Remote Play Together"